data.description: Welcome to your own personal paradise! This gem of a listing is nestled in a peaceful community with easy access to Lake Wylie and the Rock Hill Airport, perfect for outdoor enthusiasts and travelers. Step inside to find inviting hardwood floors, a chef's dream kitchen with granite countertops, wood cabinets and a tile floor, great for effortless cooking and entertaining. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the backyard oasis that will leave you in awe. Step outside and you'll find a resort style pool that promises endless hours of relaxation and enjoyment. A screened-in porch overlooks the pool, providing the perfect spot for sipping morning coffee or enjoying an evening cocktail while taking in the picturesque view. A second patio/deck area invites you to bask in the sun, read a book or simply unwind in the serene surroundings. The meticulously landscaped backyard is an envy worthy space, ideal for outdoor gatherings, barbecues and making cherished memories!
